---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Nick Sammons | North Georgia REALTOR®">
	<main class="relative z-0">
		<!-- Introduction -->
		<section class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
				<div class="relative">
					<img 
						src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/nick-headshot.jpg" 
						alt="Nick Sammons" 
						class="w-full h-[700px] object-cover grayscale shadow-2xl"
					/>
					<div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 hidden xl:block w-72 h-48 bg-stone-900 p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
						<p class="text-white text-2xl font-serif italic leading-tight text-center">Your North Georgia Partner.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-10">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest">The Realtor</span>
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif tracking-tight leading-none">Nick <span class="italic text-stone-500">Sammons.</span></h1>
					<div class="prose prose-stone font-light text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-lg space-y-6">
						<p>
							Nick Sammons is a professional REALTOR® based right here in Georgia. Born and raised in Gwinnett County, he moved to North Georgia after high school and has called it home ever since. Building on early experience in sales, he has become a standout leader in real estate.
						</p>
						<p>
							Known for his resourcefulness, discipline, and no-nonsense approach, Nick goes the extra mile every time to deliver exceptional service. He is committed to transparency, open communication, and truly listening to clients, whether it's crafting the story of their dream home or navigating a tough market.
						</p>
						<p>
							From buying and selling to rentals and investment properties, Nick handles it all with dedication and a focus on client satisfaction. Outside of real estate, Nick is an avid golfer and an ISSA Certified Personal Trainer and Nutritionist, passionate about helping others get stronger and feel their best.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Mccall Properties Info -->
		<section class="bg-stone-950 text-white py-32 px-6 lg:px-12">
			<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center space-y-12">
				<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/mccall-logo-v2.png" alt="Chris McCall Realty" class="h-16 w-auto mx-auto invert" />
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif tracking-tight">Representing <span class="italic text-stone-400">Chris McCall Realty</span></h2>
				<p class="text-stone-400 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Operating under the prestigious Chris McCall Realty banner, Nick leverages a robust network and decades of regional expertise. Chris McCall Realty is known for its deep roots in the North Georgia community and its commitment to high-integrity property transactions across residential, commercial, and investment sectors.
				</p>
				<div class="pt-10">
					<a href="/NickSammonsReality/contact" class="inline-block px-12 py-5 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white hover:text-stone-900 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transition-all">
						Partner With Us
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
